version 1.0.6 - 01.01.2022
	drop support for python2, now cout requires python version >= 3.6
version 1.0.5 - 01.07.2011
	removed default black bgcolor and grey fgcolor, because of problems with
	custom terminal color schemes
version 1.0.4 - 20.05.2009
	apply colors also to stderr
version 1.0.3 - 15.05.2009
	do not lose return value
version 1.0.2 - 13.05.2009
	added Python 2.6 support
version 1.0.1 - 04.06.2008
	no color when stdout is not a tty
	added highlight scheme for diff
version 1.0 - 27.05.2008
	support for make/gcc and svn

